name: Miah Sanchez
about: Hiiii! I'm Miah and I'm a third year computer science student. I'm really passionate about product thinking and diversity in tech and do a lot of work trying to encourage more Black and Latinx women to get into this field :) I'm also the co-president of the Underrepresented Minorities in Computing at Cornell! In my free time you can catch me editing youtube videos while eating orange chicken burrito bowls at Terrace, feel free to say hi!
